  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/05/cash-rich-nokia-invests-100-million-to-boost-connected-car-tech/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/c122eb96b90d1aa422c609611aa59769/200090655/nokiaherecarridelead02.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说有来自<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/02/microsoft-will-acquire-nokias-devices-and-services-business/\">微软的丰厚收购金</a>打底，但后手机时代的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/29/nokia-final-earnings-report-separate-company/\">诺基亚</a>还是需要发展起自己的核心业务才能生存前行。而他们旗下最赚钱的 <a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/tag/nokiahere/\">Here</a> 应用就是个很好的方向，就在昨天，诺基亚宣布将通过 NGP（Nokia Growth Partners）基金会投资一亿美元，专门用于联网车辆、地图等方面的技术创新。官方希望利用为开发此类技术公司注资的方法，来「扩大 Here 地图、定位产品相关的生态系统」。<br />\n<br />\n考虑到现在诺基亚将不再受制于 Windows Phone，原生的 Android、iOS 版 Here 应用说不定很快就会到来。而他们在 LinkedIn 上放出的两条征人启事似乎也在预示着这一点，其一是希望招聘能打造「行业领先行动 SDK」的 iOS、Android 开发者；至于第二条，则与 Android 平台上的众人绘制地图开发有关。不出意外的话，未来微软还会是 Here 或其它诺基亚应用的大客户。而对 iOS 或 Android 用户来说，多一个好用的地图选择也是可喜可贺的呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/05/cash-rich-nokia-invests-100-million-to-boost-connected-car-tech/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://company.nokia.com/en/news/press-releases/2014/05/05/nokia-launches-100-million-connected-car-fund-managed-by-nokia-growth-partners-ngp\" target=\"_blank\">PhoneArena</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://company.nokia.com/en/news/press-releases/2014/05/05/nokia-launches-100-million-connected-car-fund-managed-by-nokia-growth-partners-ngp\" target=\"_blank\">Nokia</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/jobs2/view/13532423?trk=jobs_search_public_seo_page\" target=\"_blank\">Nokia (Linkedin) (1)</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/jobs2/view/13451894?trk=jobs_biz_pub\" target=\"_blank\">(2)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/05/cash-rich-nokia-invests-100-million-to-boost-connected-car-tech/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20880449/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/05/cash-rich-nokia-invests-100-million-to-boost-connected-car-tech/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
